Mark G. Essig CPAChief Executive Officer, FireKing Security Group, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 7 different industries.See Board Relationships59--
Background

		Mr. Mark G. Essig, CPA, serves as the Chief Executive Officer at FireKing Security Group, LLC. Mr. Essig serves as the Chief Executive Officer of FKI Security Group. Mr. Essig served as the President of Shale-Inland Fabricating & Distribution Services at Shale-Inland Holdings, LLC. He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Barjan LLC (formerly, Barjan Products, LLC) from September 2002 to June 2008. He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Aviation, Power & Marine, ... Inc. from January 2009 to January 2010 and RathGibson LLC from January 2011 to May 2012. He served as the President at Barjan LLC since September 2002. He served as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President at GS Industries, Inc. from January 1998 to August 2002 and Sangamon Industries, L.L.C. from May 2008 to January 2011. He was employed at Monomoy Capital Partners and Bain Capital, LLC. He served as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President at GS Technologies Operating Co., Inc. He served as an Executive Vice President at AK Steel Corporation from 1992 to 1997. He held several positions at AK Steel including Executive Vice President of Operations and Sales from 1997 to January 1998, Executive Vice President of Sales 1994 to 1997, Vice President of Sales and Marketing from 1992 to 1994 and Assistant to CEO and Vice President of Human Resources in 1992. He served as Chief Financial Officer of Washington Steel Corporation from 1990 to 1992 and as Vice President of Finance & Administration from 1988 to 1990. He has been a Director of AK Steel Corporation and AK Steel Holding Corporation since November 1, 2013. He served as a Director of Barjan LLC. He served as a Director of Steel Technologies LLC (NuMit LLC) from 2003 to June 1, 2007. He served as a Director of GS Industries, Inc. He holds Bachelor degree from Loyola University and Master of Business Administration degree from the University of Illinois.Read Full Background




