Insider Activity


Individual




Mark G. Essig



Mr. Mark G. Essig is Independent Director at AK Steel Holding Corp. and Chief Executive Officer at FKI Security Group LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at AK Steel Holding Corp., American Iron & Steel Institute, Inc., The Steel Manufacturers Association, and AK Steel Corp.
Mr. Essig was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by GS Industries, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Aviation, Power & Marine, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Barjan LLC, a Principal by RathGibson, Inc., a Principal by Shale-Inland Acquisitions LLC, and a Principal by Washington Steel Corp. He also served on the board at Steel Technologies LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Loyola University of Chicago and an MBA from the University of Illinois.



